  "local_port": 35154,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How do I recover my Facebook account password without a recovery email or phone number?",
  "response": "Recovering your Facebook account password without a recovery email or phone number can be more challenging, but it\u2019s not impossible. Here\u2019s what you can try:\n\n---\n\n### 1. **Use Trusted Contacts**\nIf you\u2019ve set up **Trusted Contacts** in your Facebook account, you can use them to regain access:\n1. Go to the Facebook login page and click **Forgot Password?**\n2. Click **No longer have access to these?**\n3. Choose **Reveal my trusted contacts** and enter the full name of one of your trusted contacts.\n4. Facebook will provide a URL for your trusted contact. Contact them and ask them to visit the link to get a recovery code.\n5. Use the code to reset your password.\n\n---\n\n### 2. **Verify Your Identity**\nIf you don\u2019t have trusted contacts or other recovery options, Facebook may allow you to verify your identity:\n1. Go to the Facebook login page and click **Forgot Password?**\n2. Click **No longer have access to these?**\n3. Choose **I cannot access my email or phone** and then **Continue**.\n4. Follow the instructions to upload a photo ID (e.g., passport, driver\u2019s license, or national ID). Facebook will verify your identity and help you regain access.\n\n---\n\n### 3. **Check Old Emails or Phone Numbers**\nIf you\u2019ve used a different email or phone number in the past to log into Facebook:\n1. Go to the Facebook login page and click **Forgot Password?**\n2. Enter any old email address or phone number associated with your account.\n3. Follow the instructions to reset your password.\n\n---\n\n### 4. **Contact Facebook Support**\nIf none of the above methods work, visit the **Facebook Help Center** (https://www.facebook.com/help) and look for the **Recover Your Account** section. You may be able to submit a support request for further assistance.\n\n---\n\n### Tips:\n _________\n- **Secure your account once recovered**: Add a recovery email and phone number to avoid this issue in the future.\n- **Be cautious of scams**: Only use official Facebook channels for account recovery.\n\nGood luck!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
